01:07:49,307 --> 01:07:51,901
All right, I'm on the off-ramp.

1039
01:07:52,577 --> 01:07:54,306
Go right, then double back on yourself.

1040
01:07:54,412 --> 01:07:56,141
All right, I got it.

1041
01:07:58,483 --> 01:08:00,713
All right, take another right.

1042
01:08:06,157 --> 01:08:07,852
Still see him?

1043
